documentation:
Parses GitHub repo + path spec in the form of:

* {repo_owner}/{repo_name}@{ref}:{path}
* {repo_owner}/{repo_name}:{path}@{ref}
* {repo_owner}/{repo_name}:{path}
* {repo_owner}/{repo_name}/{path}
* {repo_owner}/{repo_name}/{path}@{ref}
* {repo_owner}/{repo_name}/{path}?ref={ref}
